# Image Iceberg Pipeline (UV-based)

## Stack
- UV (package manager)
- Spark + Iceberg
- S3 storage
- CV feature extraction
- CLIP embeddings

## Models
- CAMERA (AUV/UAV)
- RASTER (GeoTIFF)

## Goal
PB-scale geospatial + vision analytics lakehouse
